        ('u_vendor_eval_docs', 'Do your procurements documents outline cybersecurity requirements and questions that are used to evaluate vendors such that, given two roughly equivalent options based on cost and functionality, the more secure option is preferred?', 'C6.03', 'Procurement Documents: the paperwork detailing the contractual relationship between a customer and a supplier of goods or services', 'Supply Chain Risk Management', 'C6', 'SCRM', 'Security Scorecards is a collection of security health metrics for open source, allowing users to evaluate the security practices of an open source package before use.', 'OpenSSF: Scorecards', 'tool', 'https://github.com/ossf/scorecard'),
