        ('u_regular_backups', 'Do you back up all business critical systems at a regular cadence, no less than once per year, and are these backups stored separately from the source systems?', 'C7.04', null, 'Incident Response', 'C7', 'IR', 'This tool sets up automatic backups of Windows 10 and 11 operating systems.', 'Windows Auto Backup', 'tool', 'https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/back-up-your-windows-pc-87a81f8a-78fa-456e-b521-ac0560e32338')
